body.description: Chris Jericho’s notable rockstar persona in the wrestling world is recreated for AEW and wrestling fans alike! AEW’s first-ever “Le Champion,” the wrestling legend is captured here in his authentically styled entrance jackets, sunglasses, and bandana. With his limited edition 6.5-inch collectible figure, you can dream up your favorite AEW match-up and have a blast using the accessories included with the figure, like the AEW microphone and swappable alternate hands to declare victory! Featuring character-authentic details and wrestling gear, Jericho’s action figure is also well-articulated, boasting 25 points of articulation, perfect for posing, playing, and displaying. The complete AEW Unrivaled collection includes other fan-favorite wrestling figures, with each collectible styled from the AEW Dynamite and PPV events! Start your AEW collection today!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: About AWE Founded by CEO, GM and Head of Creative Tony Khan, AEW is a new professional wrestling league headlined by Cody & Brandi Rhodes, Kenny Omega, The Young Bucks (Matt & Nick Jackson) Chris Jericho, Sting, Hangman Page and Jon Moxley. For the first time in many years, AEW is offering an alternative to mainstream wrestling, with a roster of world-class talent that is injecting new spirit, freshness and energy to the industry. The inaugural event under the AEW banner was the sold-out DOUBLE OR NOTHING AEW All Elite Wrestling Chris Jericho Action Figure, 6.5” - Plus Accessories Recreate your favorite matchup with Chris Jericho’s 6.5-inch collectible figure from Jazwares’ AEW Unrivaled Collection! The complete AEW Unrivaled collection features more of your favorite wrestling stars with each collectible boasting of 25 points of articulation. This makes them perfect for playing and then displaying! Each are also authentically styled from the AEW Dynamite and PPV events! Start your AEW collection today! With the AEW Unrivaled Collection, you can collect, play, and display your favorite AEW wrestlers! Each figure is well-articulated, making them poseable and perfect for displaying your collection. AEW fans, pro-wrestling fans, action figure collectors, and toy enthusiasts will love the true-to-life details of the AEW Unrivaled Collection as well as the authentic accessories!

All Elite Wrestling Universe Enter the AEW Universe with the best pro-wrestling action figures out there! Every AEW action figure features one true-to-life accessory to create a truly authentic play and display experience! Playable & Displayable With meticulous details and incredible features, the AEW action figures can help recreate your AEW dream match-up! An Officially Licensed AEW Product! An officially licensed AEW product by Jazwares!

About Jazwares Jazwares, a subsidiary of Alleghany Capital Corporation, specializes in consumer products including toys, plush, action figures, collectibles and musical instruments. Jazwares’ portfolio includes a variety of dynamic licensed and wholly owned brands. With over 20 years of design, development, and manufacturing experience, Jazwares is a company with a progressive focus on identifying new trends and transforming them into high-quality products for consumers of all ages. Jazwares, which is headquartered in Sunrise, FL, has offices around the world and sells in over 100 countries. Since its inception in 1997, Jazwares continues to grow through the development of new products and the strategic acquisitions of companies like First Act, Russ Berrie, Zag Toys, Wicked Cool Toys and Kellytoy.
